query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS baseball_stats (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  playerId INT NOT NULL,
  season INT NOT NULL,
  gamesPlayed INT DEFAULT 0,
  atBats INT DEFAULT 0,
  runs INT DEFAULT 0,
  hits INT DEFAULT 0,
  doubles INT DEFAULT 0,
  triples INT DEFAULT 0,
  homeRuns INT DEFAULT 0,
  rbi INT DEFAULT 0,
  stolenBases INT DEFAULT 0,
  walks INT DEFAULT 0,
  strikeouts INT DEFAULT 0,
  battingAvg DECIMAL(4,3) DEFAULT 0,
  obp DECIMAL(4,3) DEFAULT 0,
  slg DECIMAL(4,3) DEFAULT 0,
  ops DECIMAL(4,3) DEFAULT 0,
  inningsPitched DECIMAL(5,1) DEFAULT 0,
  wins INT DEFAULT 0,
  losses INT DEFAULT 0,
  saves INT DEFAULT 0,
  era DECIMAL(4,2) DEFAULT 0,
  whip DECIMAL(4,2) DEFAULT 0,
  pitchingStrikeouts INT DEFAULT 0,
  pitchingWalks INT DEFAULT 0,
  fastballVelo INT,
  curveballVelo INT,
  changeupVelo INT,
  exitVelo INT,
  popTime DECIMAL(3,2),
  sixtyYardDash DECIMAL(3,2),
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)
